        <!-- Content Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
          <!-- Left Side - Text Content -->
          <div class="mt-8 md:mt-12">
            <p class="text-[13.5px] md:text-[15.5px] text-gray-600 leading-relaxed tracking-wide font-light antialiased">
              As businesses increasingly adopt Data Science, Artificial Intelligence, and Machine Learning, the demand for skilled professionals has grown rapidly. However, many professionals struggle to gain practical, job-ready expertise. Corpnce was founded to bridge this critical skills gap. We are one of the leading Data Science, AI, and Machine Learning training institutes in Bangalore, offering industry-focused programs for students, working professionals, and enterprises. What makes Corpnce different is our project-driven training approach. Our programs emphasize hands-on projects, real datasets, and practical problem-solving that simulate real industry use cases. Our training is delivered by experienced Data Science and AI professionals with strong industry backgrounds, helping learners understand how ML models, AI systems, and data pipelines are built and used in production.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Right Side - TQ Comparison Bar Graph -->
          <div class="relative h-full min-h-[400px] flex items-center justify-center mt-8 md:mt-12">
            <div class="relative w-full h-full rounded-2xl p-8 bg-white border border-gray-100 hover:border-yellow-400 transition-all duration-500 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-yellow-400/10">
              <!-- Bar Chart Container -->
              <div class="relative h-48 sm:h-56 md:h-64 flex items-end justify-center gap-4 sm:gap-6 md:gap-8 lg:gap-12 pt-6 sm:pt-8 min-w-0" id="tq-chart-container">
